'[[Sailing|Sailing/Yachting]]' is an Olympic sport starting from the Games of
the 1 st Olympiad (1896 Olympics in Athens ). With the exception of
1904 and possible 1916 sailing was always a part of the Olympic program. The
Sailing program of 1992 consisted of a total of ten sailing classes
(disciplines). For each class races were scheduled from July 27, 1992 to August
4, 1992 of the coast of Barcelona, Spain on the Mediterranean Sea
